WEBVTT

00:01:58.440 --> 00:02:01.640
and to double per capita incomes
in one generation.

00:02:02.520 --> 00:02:04.576
And yet today,

00:02:04.600 --> 00:02:06.696
the largest emerging economies --

00:02:06.720 --> 00:02:09.416
countries with at least
50 million people --

00:02:09.440 --> 00:02:12.920
continue to struggle to reach
that seven percent magic mark.

00:02:13.760 --> 00:02:14.976
Worse than that,

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:19.616
countries like India, Russia,
South Africa, Brazil and even China

00:02:19.640 --> 00:02:22.136
are falling below
that seven percent number

00:02:22.160 --> 00:02:25.000
and, in many cases, actually regressing.

00:02:25.800 --> 00:02:27.720
Economic growth matters.

00:02:28.440 --> 00:02:29.896
With economic growth,

00:02:29.920 --> 00:02:34.096
countries and societies
enter into a virtuous cycle